| firstName | lastName | address | city     | state    | zip    | phoneNumber | email          |
+-----------+----------+---------+----------+----------+--------+-------------+----------------+
| Bhaskar   | navi     | nellore | Anellore | AP       |  57024 |      676768 | Bhas@gmail.com |
| sam       | n        | ooty    | ooty     | TN       |  57025 |      676769 | sam@gmail.com  |
| Siddiq    | Khan     | bani    | Mysore   | Karnatka | 570017 |      676767 | sid@gmail.com  |
