+-----------+----------+---------+-----------+----------+--------+-------------+----------------+
2 rows in set (0.00 sec)


UC6: Ability to Retrieve Person belonging to a City or State from the Address Book
mysql> insert into addressBook (firstName, lastName, address, city, state, zip, phoneNumber, email) VALUES
    -> ('sam', 'n', 'ooty', 'ooty', 'Tn', 570017, 767676, 'sam@gmail.com');
Query OK, 1 row affected (0.31 sec)

mysql> select * from addressBook;
+-----------+----------+---------+-----------+----------+--------+-------------+----------------+
| firstName | lastName | address | city      | state    | zip    | phoneNumber | email          |
+-----------+----------+---------+-----------+----------+--------+-------------+----------------+
| Bhaskar   | navi     | nellore | Hyderabad | AP       |  57024 |      676768 | Bhas@gmail.com |
| sam       | n        | ooty    | ooty      | Tn       | 570017 |      767676 | sam@gmail.com  |
| Siddiq    | Khan     | bani    | Mysore    | Karnatka | 570017 |      676767 | sid@gmail.com  |
+-----------+----------+---------+-----------+----------+--------+-------------+----------------+
3 rows in set (0.10 sec)

mysql> select * from addressBook where city = 'Mysore';
